Package net.atos.testeatos.services

Contains the service classes used by the application.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EmployeeRestService
    Defines data management operations to the system's repository that can be used by EmployeeRestController to manage the repository through REST endpoints.
    EmployeeService
    Defines data access operations to the system's repository that can be used by EmployeeController to return lists of {@link net.atos.testeatos.model.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EmployeeRestServiceImpl
    Service class that implements the .EmployeeService EmployeeRestService interface.
    EmployerServiceImpl
    Service class that implements the .EmployeeService EmployeeService interface.

Package net.atos.testeatos.services Description

Contains the service classes used by the application. They define interfaces which the controller classes can use to access the repository's data, as well as implementations of said interfaces.
